room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Hidden Key Escapes in Chicago
room_description: As a group of tenacious treasure hunters, you're on a mission to find that one invaluable prize. Unfortunately, you have to steal it. The Museum has a precious Peruvian artifact sitting in their basement storage room until it can be appraised and put on display. You're inside man has helped you gain access to the storage room...now you must find the artifact before the guards return on patrol. Will you steal the artifact, or get caught red handed?
